ra Kumar Upadhyay\n|Christopher French, [[Daler Mehndi]]\n|-\n|''Aye Zindagi''\n|\"Aye Zindagi Single\"\n|[[Sonu Nigam]], [[Asha Bhosle]], [[Alka Yagnik]], [[Suresh Wadkar]], [[Shaan (singer)|Shaan]], [[Abhijeet Bhattacharya]] \n|[[Rashmi Virag]]\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"22\"|2019\n|rowspan=\"6\"|''[[Notebook (2019 film)|Notebook]]''\n|\"Nai Lagda\"\n|Vishal Mishra, [[Asees Kaur]]\n|Akshay Tripathi\n|rowspan=\"6\"| Solo composer\n|-\n|\"Laila\"\n|Dhvani Bhanushali\n|Vishal Mishra, Abhendra Kumar Upadhyay\n|-\n|\"Bhumro\"\n|[[Kamaal Khan]], Vishal Mishra\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Kaushal Kishore\n|-\n|\"Safar\"\n|[[Mohit Chauhan]]\n|-\n|\"Main Taare\"\n|[[Salman Khan]]\n|[[Manoj Muntashir]]\n|-\n|\"Notebook Epilogue\"\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Vishal Mishra\n|Instrumental \n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Kabir Singh]]''\n|\"Kaise Hua\"\n|Manoj Muntashir\n|rowspan=2|Sachet-Parampara, [[Mithoon]], [[Amaal Mallik]], [[Akhil Sachdeva]]\n|-\n|\"Pehla Pyaar\"\n|[[Armaan Malik]]\n|[[Irshad Kamil]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3|''[[Jabariya Jodi]]''\n|Ki Honda Pyaar (Male)\n|[[Arijit Singh]]\n|rowspan=3|Raj Shekhar\n|rowspan=3|[[Tanishk Bagchi]], Sachet-Parampara, Ashok Mastie, Ramji Gulati\n|-\n|Ki Honda Pyaar (Female)\n|[[Neha Kakkar]], Vishal Mishra\n|-\n|Macchardani\n|Vishal Mishra, [[Jyotica Tangri]]\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[Pranaam]]\n|Sirf Tu\n|Armaan Malik\n|rowspan=4|Manoj Muntashir\n|rowspan=4|Jaan Nisar\n|-\n|Zindagi\n|[[Ankit Tiwari]]\n|-\n|Jai Hanuman\n|[[Sukhwinder Singh]]\n|-\n|Illahi\n|[[Sonu Nigam]]\n|-\n|rowspan=7|''[[Saand Ki Aankh]]''\n|Udta Teetar\n|Vishal Mishra Ft. Sunidhi Chauhan & Nooran Sisters\n|rowspan=8|Raj Shekhar\n|rowspan=\"8\"|Solo composer\n|-\n|-\n|Womaniya\n|Vishal Mishra Ft. Vishal Dadlani\n|-\n|Aasmaa\n|Vishal Mishra Ft. Asha Bhosle\n|-\n|Baby Gold\n|Vishal Mishra Ft. Sona Mohapatra & Jyotica Tangri\n|-\n|Jhunna Jhunna\n|Vishal Mishra Ft. Pratibha Singh Baghel & Krutika Borkar\n|-\n|Womaniya (Raw Version)\n|rowspan=2|Vishal Mishra\n|-\n|Aasmaa (Studio Version)\n|-\n|rowspan=5|2020\n|style=\"